The paper discusses the coordination of information provided by multiple experts using belief networks, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the combination of probabilities and graphs, which are topics in information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS).
